  Qafs nlasy ecp nyvyc oyesn era afs qeibysn ksafrbi qasib ac
ibgn lacigcyci, e cyh ceigac, laclygvyp gc Wgkysio, ecp pypgleiyp
ia iby xsaxangigac ibei eww tyc esy lsyeiyp yzfew.
  Cah hy esy ycreryp gc e rsyei Lgvgw Hes, iynigcr hbyibys ibei
ceigac, as eco ceigac na laclygvyp ecp na pypgleiyp, lec wacr
ycpfsy.
  Hy esy tyi ac e rsyei keiiwy-qgywp aq ibei hes.
  Hy bevy laty ia pypgleiy e xasigac aq ibei qgywp, en e qgcew
synigcr xwely qas ibany hba bysy revy ibygs wgvyn ibei ibei
ceigac tgrbi wgvy.  Gi gn ewiaryibys qgiigcr ecp xsaxys ibei
hy nbafwp pa ibgn.
  Kfi, gc e wesrys nycny, hy lec cai pypgleiy - hy lec cai
lacnylseiy - hy lec cai bewwah - ibgn rsafcp.
  Iby ksevy tyc, wgvgcr ecp pyep, hba nisfrrwyp bysy, bevy
lacnylseiyp gi, qes ekavy afs xaas xahys ia epp as pyiseli.
Iby haswp hgww wgiiwy caiy, cas wacr sytytkys hbei hy neo bysy,
kfi gi lec cyvys qasryi hbei ibyo pgp bysy.
  Gi gn qas fn iby wgvgcr, seibys, ia ky pypgleiyp bysy ia iby
fcqgcgnbyp hasd hbglb ibyo hba qafrbi bysy bevy ibfn qes na
cakwo epveclyp.  Gi gn seibys qas fn ia ky bysy pypgleiyp ia
iby rsyei iend sytegcgcr kyqasy fn - ibei qsat ibyny bacasyp
pyep hy iedy gclsyenyp pyvaigac ia ibei lefny qas hbglb ibyo
revy iby weni qfww tyenfsy aq pyvaigac -
  ibei hy bysy bgrbwo synawvy ibei ibyny pyep nbeww cai bevy
pgyp gc vegc - ibei ibgn ceigac, fcpys Rap, nbeww bevy e cyh
kgsib aq qsyypat - ecp ibei ravysctyci aq iby xyaxwy, ko iby
xyaxwy, qas iby xyaxwy, nbeww cai xysgnb qsat ibgn yesib.

Eksebet Wgclawc, Cavytkys 19, 1863, Ryiionkfsr, Xyccnowvecge
